bookTitle: Charlotte and the Seven Frat Brothers
Plot: Charlotte Withers is a senior in college. When the dorm rooms are filled to capacity, Charlotte has to stay one semester at a frat house, where she meets the Seven Frat Brothers. She doesn't mind, nearly as much since this is her last year and then she is off to her dream job in LA. Follow Charlotte through a journey of discovering herself. Witness hilarious instant messenger convos and so much more.
